setpassword to the root user
sudo passwd root

Creating - low level user
sudo adduser <lowleveluser>
set password and Full Name -Y
usermod -aG sudo <lowleveluser>

Create a standard user
sudo useradd -m <standardusername>
sudo usermod -a -G sudo <standardusername>
sudo chsh -s/bin/bash <standardusername>


